{"tid":1648923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家真係唔嬲咩","createTime":"2019-10-12T12:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T12:58:18.000Z","uid":6741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"209a5e74df8b034e55e99188dd6b5ab2cb0e9f65","tid":1648923,"uid":6741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"15歲女仔 俾人全裸棄屍 <br />\n單係狗同所謂法醫嘅判斷<br />\n就話無可疑 然後火化毀屍滅跡<br />\n<br />\n加埋 中大女義士 被施暴勇敢出嚟指證狗嘅暴行<br />\n一個男仔比人強姦雞姦 受盡極非人道對待<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家真係接受到咩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋經歷咗一個好漫長嘅夏天<br />\n好多義士受傷流血<br />\n我哋嘅朋友比人拉 受虐打 甚至殘廢<br />\n<br />\n政府草菅人命<br />\n官員公然講大話 獨善其身<br />\n警察目無皇法 殘害市民 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家真係忍到咩?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我已經忍夠啦<br />\n所有憤怒嘅香港人<br />\n同我一樣<br />\n唔會再忍受呢個不公嘅社會</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋要改變呢個荒謬嘅香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">拒絕禁蒙面<br />\n拒絕被捕<br />\n拒絕打壓自由</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8e90799de78e66b0d6b2653b163b540f3f2f8f2","tid":1648923,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n香港人真 &middot; 反抗！！！<br />\n<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669】＜\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669】＜</a></div></ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"b808e0049eb5f985606f65aecbf0fa5588e212fa","tid":1648923,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpe